          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='16'>Æ </run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#1f2a40' fontname='Lucida Fax' fontsize='16'>KEY INSIGHTS</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#1f2a40' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Negative-sentiment titles average 3.61M views — nearly 2x higher than Neutral (1.85M) — suggesting provocative titles may drive more clicks.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#1f2a40' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Trending video volume held steady from December through May, with the lower counts in November and June reflecting partial-month data at the dataset&apos;s edges rather than an actual decline.</run>
          </formatted-text>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#1f2a40' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
