            <run fontcolor='#1f2a40' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Sentiment classified using VADER (Valence Aware Dictionary and sEntiment Reasoner) applied to video titles, with scores grouped into Positive, Neutral, and Negative categories. Dataset covers ~178,580 trending video records across five countries (US, GB, IN, JP, DE), from </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#1f2a40' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>14-11-2017</run>
            <run fontcolor='#1f2a40' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> to </run>
